#
# Server-side
<reply>
<servercmd>
AUTH DIGEST-MD5 PLAIN
REPLY "AUTH DIGEST-MD5" + Rubbish
REPLY * -ERR AUTH exchange cancelled by client
REPLY "AUTH PLAIN" +
REPLY dXNlcgB1c2VyAHNlY3JldA== +OK Login successful
</servercmd>
<data>
From: me@somewhere
To: fake@nowhere

body

--
  yours sincerely
</data>
</reply>

